            Star, Clock, DollarSign, ChevronRight, Filter, MoreHorizontal,
            Send, Paperclip, Phone, Mail, CheckCircle, X, Menu, Briefcase,
            Camera, PenTool, Code, Truck, BookOpen, Smartphone, Monitor,
